<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Supprimer un client - Hôtel California</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>

<body class="bg-gray-50 flex flex-col min-h-screen">
    <nav class="bg-gray-800 text-white p-4">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
            <h1 class="text-xl font-bold">Hotel California</h1>
            <ul class="flex gap-6">
                 <li><a href="/" class="hover:underline">Accueil</a></li>
                <li><a href="/chambres" class="hover:underline">Chambres</a></li>
                <li><a href="/reservations" class="hover:underline">Réservations</a></li>
                <li><a href="/clients" class="hover:underline">Clients</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>
    
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-6 flex-1 w-full">
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Supprimer un client</h1>

            <div class="bg-white border p-6">
                <p class="mb-2"><strong>Nom : </strong><%= client.nom %></p>
                <p class="mb-2"><strong>Téléphone : </strong><%= client.telephone %></p>
                <p class="mb-2"><strong>Email : </strong><%= client.email %></p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Nombre de personnes : </strong><%= client.nbPersonnes %></p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Êtes-vous sûr de vouloir supprimer ce client ?</strong></p>

                <form action="/clients/<%= client.idClient %>/delete" method="post">
                    <div class="flex gap-2">
                        <a href="/clients" class="bg-gray-800 text-white px-4 py-2 hover:bg-gray-700">Annuler</a>
                        <button type="submit" class="bg-red-600 text-white px-4 py-2 hover:bg-red-700">Supprimer</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <footer class="bg-gray-800 text-white p-4 mt-8">
            <p>&copy; 2025 Hôtel California. Tous droits réservés.</p>
        </footer>
</body>

</html>